WHAT THE ORGANISATION DOES:
The charity works to make later life as fulfilling as possible regardless of personal circumstances.  It achieves this for older people and their family carers  through providing information and advice, care and support services, and campaigning with and for them.

ORGANISATION CONTEXT:
HOLLOW ROAD, BURY ST. EDMUNDS, IP32 7FA, Suffolk, Suffolk. ~25 staff; income on record £2,131,722.

