We support LGBTQ* young people aged 30 and under in Cambridgeshire, Peterborough and surrounding areas. We deliver programmes in youth work, schools, training and consultancy.

ORGANISATION CONTEXT:
Ely / Cambridge & Peterborough, Cambridgeshire. ~16 staff; income on record £666,694.

RECOMMENDED VAxAI ENTRY: Blend: training + workflow review

WHY ADMIN / AI PRESSURE IS HIGH:
Youth support, schools, training, consultancy and safeguarding are growing from small to mid-size. Strong need for scalable CRM, scheduling, policy and reporting workflows.

CHARITY / SECTOR AI CONTEXT (use in conversation):
Youth charities often juggle CRM or case tools with heavy manual reporting to councils and funders. AI for programme summaries and parent communications is emerging but needs clear policy.

